snippet: Adrienne Motley scored a season-high 22 points on 8-of-13 shooting and No. 13 Miami cruised to a 69-49 win over Florida International on Friday night....
lead_paragraph: Adrienne Motley scored a season-high 22 points on 8-of-13 shooting and No. 13 Miami cruised to a 69-49 win over Florida International on Friday night.

headline.main: Motley Scores 22, No. 13 Miami Women Beat FIU 69-49
